comment: Muscala (ATL) bumps Butler (CHI) and causes him to lose control of the ball.
Butler (CHI) does not cause Daye (ATL) to lose control of the ball with the contact.
Brand (ATL) has his hand on Gasol's (CHI) hip but the contact does not affect his shot attempt.
CHI does not reenter the court in a timely manner.
Mirotic (CHI) makes incidental contact with Brand (ATL) as he attempts to secure the rebound.
Mirotic (CHI) faces up with Muscala (ATL) and holds him as he attempts to secure the rebound.
